description._content: TITLE Tilden, George of Keene NH CREATOR SUBJECT Men - NH - Keene Business people, American - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION Photograph of George Tilden of Keene New Hampshire. He was born 4/21/1802 in Marshfield MA and came to Keene in 1817. He learned the bookbinders trade and went into business for himself in 1825. He published the North American Spelling Book and other books and was also active in Keene's savings banks. In 1825 he married Harriet Wyman of Keene and they had 4 children. He died 11/3/1888.
